##DESCRIPTION
## Related rates -- a snowball problem;  find the rate at which the volume
##  is decreasing given the rate at which the diameter is deacreasing and the
##  value for the diameter.
##ENDDESCRIPTION
##KEYWORDS('derivatives', 'related rates')

